MPC

Enum TokenOp

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TokenOp>
      • MPC.TokenOp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TokenOp>, Token

    public enum TokenOp
extends java.lang.Enum<TokenOp>
implements Token
    Represents all operator tokens in the Pascal language that are used in OO Mini-Pascal as defined by the Extended Pascal ISO document.
